casebody.data:
FRANK VANDEVER v. COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION (AC 22933)

Lavery, C. J., and Foti and Flynn, Js.

Submitted on briefs May 2 officially released June 10, 2003 Per Curiam.

The habeas court did not abuse its discretion in denying the petition for certification to appeal from the dismissal of the petition for a writ of habeas corpus.

The appeal is dismissed.
